reviewText: This is another review I am writing about a Shu Qi movie I bought a long time ago. I have quite a few, and I like them all , some more than others. I know I did not have a problem with this one, though I cannot say what it was about without watching it again. And I will. Just want this review request gone.

I found this movie to be very entertaiming. I feel Shu Qi is a very Diverse actress; who has really blossomed as a star. She can play comedic roles well; as well as dramatic roles; such as this movie. This movie has a good script; as well as stunts. Tony D.
